{"thag6.4:0.1":"Theragatha 6.4 ","thag6.4:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.4:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.4:0.4":"Kullattheragatha ","thag6.4:1.1":"“Kullo sivathikam gantva, ","thag6.4:1.2":"addasa itthimujjhitam; ","thag6.4:1.3":"Apaviddham susanasmim, ","thag6.4:1.4":"khajjantim kimihi phutam. ","thag6.4:2.1":"Aturam asucim putim, ","thag6.4:2.2":"passa kulla samussayam; ","thag6.4:2.3":"Uggharantam paggharantam, ","thag6.4:2.4":"balanam abhinanditam. ","thag6.4:3.1":"Dhammadasam gahetvana, ","thag6.4:3.2":"nanadassanapattiya; ","thag6.4:3.3":"Paccavekkhim imam kayam, ","thag6.4:3.4":"tuccham santarabahiram. ","thag6.4:4.1":"Yatha idam tatha etam, ","thag6.4:4.2":"yatha etam tatha idam; ","thag6.4:4.3":"Yatha adho tatha uddham, ","thag6.4:4.4":"yatha uddham tatha adho. ","thag6.4:5.1":"Yatha diva tatha rattim, ","thag6.4:5.2":"yatha rattim tatha diva; ","thag6.4:5.3":"Yatha pure tatha paccha, ","thag6.4:5.4":"yatha paccha tatha pure. ","thag6.4:6.1":"Pancangikena turiyena, ","thag6.4:6.2":"Na rati hoti tadisi; ","thag6.4:6.3":"Yatha ekaggacittassa, ","thag6.4:6.4":"Samma dhammam vipassato”ti. ","thag6.4:6.5":"… Kullo thero …. "}